The gateway handles:
- Request validation
- API key handling
- Payload translation
- Response normalization

---

## Requirements

- Docker + Docker Compose  
  OR
- Python 3.10+
- Ollama installed and running

---

## Quick Start (Docker)

1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/RickCreator87/AIGateway-Ollama.git
cd AIGateway-Ollama